extendedInfo.description: *** You must have LauncherPro or ADW installed.  Please read the full description before purchasing or rating. ***Don't stop at theming your LauncherPro dock.  This app takes the awesomeness of the True White Custom Launcher Icons set and wraps 370 of the best icons up as a LauncherPro Icon Pack to theme your home screen and your app drawer.It works equally well with ADW Launcher and ADW EX.  It is the perfect companion to Custom Launcher Icons.We will be updating the app frequently with more icons.  We have about 370 lined up to be added over the next couple of weeks.  You can request/vote up more icons at bit.ly/lpicons.

reviews.title: Nice. My app drawer and home screen look slick.
reviews.comment: Most of my apps are covered. I\'ve hidden the few that aren\'t.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Doesn\'t work properly
reviews.comment: I just bought this pack and it seems that it doesn\'t work correctly. Not all of my icons have changed when I applied in the menu \"Theme setting\" the pack. For example the clock application icon didn\'t change (like on the screenshot) ! So it is pretty ugly because some icons have changed and some others didn\'t ! Waste my money
reviews.author: A Google User
